These two new Creator Packs are releasing on the 3rd of December, around 10AM CET!

Reach for the sky with the Creator Pack ‘Skyscrapers’. Designed by community creator ‘REV0’. This pack introduces a bold collection of towering buildings that will transform the skyline of your city. Paying tribute to international architectural styles, it features a selection of stunning high-rises that offer a range of city service upgrades.

Included in ‘Skyscrapers’ by ‘REV0’: 

15 Signature Buildings, 2 Unique Service Buildings, 23 Accompanying Upgrades, and 3 Props

From sleek commercial headquarters to towering residential complexes. Each skyscraper in this pack is crafted to bring both form and function. Many come with several upgrade options, ranging from integrated transit terminals, rooftop observatories, and expansive underground facilities, ensuring these architectural giants are as efficient as they are iconic. With structures soaring up to 600 meters, ‘Skyscrapers’ gives your city the vertical edge it deserves.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bilal.derky.9

Lyrics | كلمات

"يلي بعدك مافي غالي
ولا قبلك عدى عليي
تسواك الروح وكل مالي
بعطيك قلبي لو بإيديي

يا عيوني الحب انا ما عرفتو
لو ما عيونا شافو عينيي
وخطفولي قلبي وما ردو
لما بأيدا سرقتلي إيديي

يا ويلي عليها
شو حلوة عنيها
سرقتني وسرقة قلبي بلحظة وقعت انا فيها
آه يا ويلي عليها
شوفو كحل عنيها
شوفو كل تفصيل بوشا الضحكة ورمشا وشالا يلي مخبيها

وعلى بيت الزينة دلوني
وبخصلة شعرا جدلوني
وحد حفة بيتا غفوني
لحتى تحن يوم عليا

وانا شفت عيونك نادوني
كيف بعد النظرة يردوني
مين يملا عيونك يا عيوني
لو ما انا مليتا بعينيا

ويا ويلي منك يا بنية
على مهلك خفي شوية
على كحلك ميت شي مية
وانا اول مين مات بحبا

تعو حطو الكون كلو قبالا
انا بيع الدنية برسمالا
يخسا القلب يلي ما يختارا
وخاب لو مال بحربا
يا ويلي عليها
شو حلوة عنيها
سرقتني وسرقة قلبي بلحظة وقعت انا فيها
آه يا ويلي عليها
شوفو كحل عنيها
شوفو كل تفصيل بوشا الضحكة ورمشا وشالا يلي مخبيها"

snippet.title: GOAT – New Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
He’s about to change the game. 

From the artists that made KPop Demon Hunters, Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse, and producer Stephen Curry, #GOATmovie is exclusively in movie theatres February 2026.

Visit our site: https://goat.movie/
Find your team: https://theroarleague.com/

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.instagram.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.tiktok.com/@goatmovieofficial
https://x.com/the_goat_movie

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

From Sony Pictures Animation, the studio behind Spider-ManTM: Across the Spider-Verse and the artists that made KPop Demon Hunters, comes GOAT, an original action-comedy set in an all-animal world. The story follows Will, a small goat with big dreams who gets a once-in-a-lifetime shot to join the pros and play roarball – a high-intensity, co-ed, full-contact sport dominated by the fastest, fiercest animals in the world. Will’s new teammates aren’t thrilled about having a little goat on their roster, but Will is determined to revolutionize the sport and prove once and for all that “smalls can ball!”
 
Directed by:​​
Tyree Dillihay
 
Co-Directed by: 
​​Adam Rosette​
 
Written by:​​
